table_description: Users in the Google Workspace domain.

columns.name: id
columns.description: The unique ID of the user.

columns.name: primaryEmail
columns.description: The primary email address of the user.

columns.name: password
columns.description: Password associated with the user.

columns.name: hashFunction
columns.description: Hash function used to store the password.

columns.name: isAdmin
columns.description: Indicates if the user is an administrator.

columns.name: isDelegatedAdmin
columns.description: Indicates if the user is a delegated administrator.

columns.name: agreedToTerms
columns.description: Indicates if the user has agreed to the terms of service.

columns.name: suspended
columns.description: Indicates if the user's account is suspended.

columns.name: changePasswordAtNextLogin
columns.description: Indicates if the user needs to change their password at the next login.

columns.name: ipWhitelisted
columns.description: Indicates if the user is IP whitelisted.

columns.name: name
columns.description: The name of the user, including given name and family name.

columns.name: kind
columns.description: Resource kind identifier, typically 'admin#directory#user'.

columns.name: etag
columns.description: ETag of the resource.

columns.name: emails
columns.description: Email addresses associated with the user.

columns.name: externalIds
columns.description: External IDs associated with the user.

columns.name: relations
columns.description: Relationships associated with the user.

columns.name: aliases
columns.description: Email aliases for the user.

columns.name: isMailboxSetup
columns.description: Indicates if the user's mailbox is set up.

columns.name: customerId
columns.description: The customer ID associated with the user.

columns.name: addresses
columns.description: Addresses associated with the user.

columns.name: organizations
columns.description: Organizations associated with the user.

columns.name: lastLoginTime
columns.description: Timestamp of the user's last login.

columns.name: phones
columns.description: Phone numbers associated with the user.

columns.name: suspensionReason
columns.description: Reason for suspending the user's account.

columns.name: thumbnailPhotoUrl
columns.description: URL to the user's thumbnail photo.

columns.name: languages
columns.description: Languages spoken by the user.

columns.name: posixAccounts
columns.description: POSIX account information associated with the user.

columns.name: creationTime
columns.description: Timestamp when the user was created.

columns.name: nonEditableAliases
columns.description: Non-editable aliases for the user.

columns.name: sshPublicKeys
columns.description: SSH public keys associated with the user.

columns.name: notes
columns.description: Notes associated with the user.

columns.name: websites
columns.description: Websites associated with the user.

columns.name: locations
columns.description: Locations associated with the user.

columns.name: includeInGlobalAddressList
columns.description: Indicates if the user is included in the global address list.

columns.name: keywords
columns.description: Keywords associated with the user.

columns.name: deletionTime
columns.description: Timestamp when the user's account was deleted.

columns.name: gender
columns.description: Gender information associated with the user.

columns.name: thumbnailPhotoEtag
columns.description: ETag for the user's thumbnail photo.

columns.name: ims
columns.description: Instant messaging service accounts associated with the user.

columns.name: customSchemas
columns.description: Custom schema information associated with the user.

columns.name: isEnrolledIn2Sv
columns.description: Indicates if the user is enrolled in two-step verification.

columns.name: isEnforcedIn2Sv
columns.description: Indicates if two-step verification is enforced for the user.

columns.name: archived
columns.description: Indicates if the user account is archived.

columns.name: orgUnitPath
columns.description: The organizational unit path for the user.

columns.name: recoveryEmail
columns.description: The user's recovery email address.

columns.name: recoveryPhone
columns.description: The user's recovery phone number.
